topic.title: Nutrition Assessment - conformance rules

section.p: This template represents the patient's nutrition abilities and habits including intake, diet requirements or diet followed.

ol.li:
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] templateId ( CONF:1098-30326, CONF:1098-30327 ) such that it
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @root="2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.138"
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="OBS" Observation (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.6 HL7ActClass) (CONF:1098-30324)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @moodCode="EVN" Event (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.1001 HL7ActMood) (CONF:1098-30325)
SHALL contain at least one [1..*] id (CONF:1098-30328)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] code (CONF:1098-30329)/@code="75303-8" Nutrition assessment (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.6.1 LOINC) (CONF:1098-32784, CONF:1098-32785)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] statusCode (CONF:1098-30332)/@code="completed" Completed (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.14 ActStatus) (CONF:1098-30333)
